CustomField.description: This setting allows us to select the names and order of the Dealmaker Tabs and Launchpad items. The value of this field should be a comma separated list of Tab names. This field should only be used by TAS group administrators.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This setting allows us to select the names and order of the Dealmaker Tabs and Launchpad items. The value of this field should be a comma separated list of Tab names. This field should only be used by TAS group administrators.
CustomField.label: Tab Name List
